{"tid":2149521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"總裁判官蘇惠德上周五批出手令 涵蓋19間公司商業紀錄、會計人事文件及數碼檔案","createTime":"2020-08-10T12:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T17:30:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":85,"dislike":105,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"9c51ce5287713b15da5e711a6d31bb71cbe02482","tid":2149521,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:43:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/JALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FJALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=227857ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FJALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM%2F&h=a5ee8db6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/JALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方今早突襲《蘋果日報》大樓並取走多箱文件，根據法庭批出的搜查令，警方獲授權進入大樓以調查有關涉嫌違反「港版國安法」的勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全罪以及串謀欺詐罪，手令涵蓋包括壹傳媒有限公司及《蘋果日報》慈善基金等19間公司，警方有權取走除新聞材料外的文件或檔案。<br />\n<br />\n搜查令申請由警員編號16281的商業罪案調查科高級督察Fung Chun-Yi提出，於8月7日由西九龍裁判法院總裁判官蘇惠德批出。手令指，有合理理由懷疑位於將軍澳工業邨駿盈街8號的蘋果日報大樓內有書本、文件、以及該些書本或文件的任何部份，相當可能對調查涉嫌違反《國安法》第29條「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國安全罪」，以及香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》的「串謀欺詐罪」有調查價值。"},{"pid":"ae5931ec6c59c4ed9bd85314a5c15abe6fb9f43a","tid":2149521,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8aadc34810afb5eb98106a70fccb12b38353c2","tid":2149521,"uid":132587,"like":172,"dislike":4,"score":168,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"20